'''Sluudrese''' or '''Sludese''' was the native language of the [[Sludir]] species from [[Sluudren]]. It was mainly formed by grunts, snorts and whinnies, making it harsh-sounding.

There was no written form for that language, and ideas had to be conveyed through intricate images. During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], written [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] replaced this activity.

Sludirs also had base-six mathematics.

Most Sludir were fluent in both Sludese and Basic, although they were only literate in their own language.

